"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-04-03-Lurking-in-shadows-for-years-Adam-Peaty-powers-to-Paris-2024-1suMMiBPNMA-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  Adam Peaty poses for a photo with his medal after winning the men's 100m breaststroke final at the British Swimming Championships in London, England, April 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999154695460177, \"rank\": 8.450177503484946e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.5851410532196198, \"rank\": 0.6253807548402189, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Adam Peaty's dominance in the men's 100m breaststroke event has been unrivaled for nearly a decade.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He showcased his supremacy by successfully defending his 100m title at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021, after earlier setting a record for the fastest 20 times in history over the distance.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The British swimmer's illustrious career includes eight World Championship gold medals, an impressive tally of 17 golds at European Championships, and four golds at the Commonwealth Games.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9999569747692212, \"rank\": 4.090195769332591e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999976295751721, \"rank\": 2.1748098478088993e-06, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the year 2022 took an unexpected turn for Peaty.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Firstly, he suffered a shocking loss, finishing fourth in the Commonwealth Games after breaking his foot.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This setback was followed by the announcement that he was caught in a \\\"self-destructive spiral,\\\" prompting him to make the stunning decision to step away from the sport in order to prioritize his mental health.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After being out of the spotlight for a long time, the 29-year-old made his return to the major tournament stage in February, where he settled for a bronze at the World Championships in Doha.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9999999999649845, \"rank\": 3.502380479544442e-11, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If that was just a warm-up, Peaty made a resounding statement on Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam Peaty during the men's 100m breaststroke final at the British Swimming Championships in London, England, April 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1513, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999154695460177, \"rank\": 8.450177503484946e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.5851410532196198, \"rank\": 0.6253807548402189, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  The two-time Olympic champion announced his comeback to the world by claiming the title at the British Championships.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With a time of 57.94 seconds in the final, he recorded the fastest men's 100m breaststroke time in the world this year.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This remarkable achievement secured his qualification for the upcoming Olympics.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the reigning world record holder with a time of 56.88 seconds, Peaty is now poised to defend his back-to-back Olympic titles in Paris.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997587565, \"rank\": 2.411711088786773e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am finding a new version of myself which I am really liking, and I think that's a version that can do really well at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so light in the water.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a real win for my team, my family and myself,\\\" Peaty said.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have learned to appreciate the moments of greatness for myself, not even relative to the world,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, that was a great swim, executed well but the most promising thing is that I am finding peace in the water now, instead of anger and just fighting it, and trying to win like that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who knows what the ending is going to be but I am having fun along the way.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It may not end up as a fairytale, but it might...\\\"  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 3023, \"entities\": []}]}"